1. extract rar to any usb, but don't put the program at any subfolder! (correct sample: f:\flowTestNewDb\)
2. there are configurable system parameters:
located at: 
f:\flowTestNewDb\sys.properties, 
f:\flowTestNewDb\mysql.db.properties, 
f:\flowTestNewDb\mssql.db.properties,
f:\flowTestNewDb\db2.db.properties
2a. change database type: 
sys.properties >> database_type=mssql
2b. for restore data: (turn off delete before insert new data):
sys.properties >>
delete_statement_generate_button_enabled=false
delete_then_restore_combo_action_enabled=false
3. backup xml data location (default):
sys.properties >>
test_folder_root=./test_folder
4. change database connection: 
mssql - f:\flowTestNewDb\mssql.db.properties
mysql - f:\flowTestNewDb\mysql.db.properties
db2 - f:\flowTestNewDb\db2.db.properties